column5: Hey all- thought I would share my version of the portable battery operated power center that I will be using on my fly ins. Fully waterproof and battery lasts a long time- it's wired for 1 12v accessory plug, 2 usb 1 outlet for my depth finder and one 1600 lumen led flood lamp and one voltmeter. Works awesome! Weighs about 14 lbs, and still plenty of room on the inside to put my delorme and my Oregon 600
